content: Singaporean actress and model **Luisa Gan** (born 12 September 1994) is a former [Singaporean](/wiki/Singaporeans) actress, model and contracted artiste under [MediaCorp](/wiki/MediaCorp). She was prominently a full-time Mediacorp artiste between 2015 and 2016. She was [Miss Singapore](/wiki/Miss_Singapore_Universe) 2014 and she has represented Singapore in the [Miss Universe](/wiki/Miss_Universe) pageant. ## Filmography YearTitleRoleNotesRef**2013**[Gonna Make It](/wiki/Gonna_Make_It_(TV_series))As herself**2015**Ghost at CaldecottLuisa[The Dream Makers II](/wiki/The_Dream_Makers_II)Portrayed Herself[Life - Fear Not](/wiki/Life_-_Fear_Not)Xia Tian**2016**[House of Fortune](/wiki/House_of_Fortune)Yang Meimei[Peace & Prosperity](/wiki/Peace_%26_Prosperity)Wati[If Only I Could](/wiki/If_Only_I_Could_(TV_series))Rachel[I Want to Be a Star](/wiki/I_Want_to_Be_a_Star)Juliet[You Can Be an Angel 2](/wiki/You_Can_Be_an_Angel_2)Su Li ## Miss Universe 2016 YearAwardResults2014Miss SingaporeWon2016Miss Universe 2016Nominated This Singaporean biographical article is a stub.
